Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照射黑暗的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.37,0:00:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說在宇宙飛舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.64,0:00:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,展開決鬥之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.41,0:00:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡的呼聲遠遠的傳開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.82,0:00:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪惡為此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.73,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換取持續戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.90,0:00:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為命運而不知所措之\N嘆息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.31,0:00:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因無法抹去的記憶\N而為愛顫抖著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.25,0:01:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照亮黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.09,0:01:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說促使得宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.13,0:01:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的墜天使們啊\N美麗的飛翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.10,0:01:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.84,0:01:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.28,0:01:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三話迷宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂小弓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.42,0:02:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，一大早的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.59,0:02:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊\N我會有很長一段時間不去上學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.46,0:02:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你跟老師說一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎拜託囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.53,0:02:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原因?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在找綾香啊，我的姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.97,0:02:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有為了維護地球的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.27,0:02:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說明的話話就長了\N我要掛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.58,0:02:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早啊，紅英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.89,0:02:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們幹嘛呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.42,0:02:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是"你們"呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做布麗姬妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是亞孃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.70,0:02:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.66,0:02:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞孃、布麗姬妲、雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.37,0:02:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼來著?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜，城琉菜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.74,0:03:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換洗的衣服準備好了\N英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.98,0:03:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不需要我們幫您換衣服嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說不必了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.69,0:03:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是被人家脫光光\N誰受得了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.06,0:03:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出不來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.46,0:03:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感應器到底怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在磨蹭什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這叫做縮頭烏龜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸，你知道怎麼用嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，真會找麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上那新的衣服過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.64,0:04:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要乖乖的等著哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.38,0:04:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也得再洗一次澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別偷看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.32,0:04:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死都不會看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.32,0:04:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那，等會見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，為什麼不是自動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.94,0:05:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好慢哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空腹正是最好的調味料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會議差不多要開始了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.51,0:05:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算做任何的說明囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有聖日耳曼城的背景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.05,0:06:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連那個機器人是由誰、\N怎麼製造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些全都是機密是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.19,0:06:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們地球戰騎隊所要求的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.20,0:06:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有對抗外星異種的所有權限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有需要\N政府各局的支援的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會主動提出請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.34,0:06:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是要我們別插手管囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.64,0:06:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為軍隊是養來幹什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.35,0:06:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從地球由單一政府統馭\N這十多年來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.65,0:06:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們人類過著\N完全沒有紛爭的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.93,0:06:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球聯合政府軍、EFA的戰力\N的確是在水準之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.86,0:06:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在實戰經驗方面\N卻存在著問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.33,0:06:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想說我們因為過得太舒服\N變得毫無用處了是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.01,0:06:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太無禮了，說話當心點\N雷文先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現實上在昨天的戰鬥中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.95,0:07:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EFA對於外星異種\N無法有效的殲滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現階段來說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.59,0:07:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將一切的戰鬥\N交給神機超重神才是最上策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.02,0:07:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信也已經實際證明過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.10,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢在此大放厥詞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.58,0:07:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想找你姊姊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.48,0:07:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是為了這個目的\N留在這座城堡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個字跡絕對是綾香的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.42,0:07:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香一定還在這座城堡的某處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.42,0:07:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那麼擔心你姊姊的安危嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.09,0:07:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你也有親人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.20,0:07:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是突然間斷了音訊\N你不會擔心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯... 我會怎樣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼你會吧你，你啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.51,0:08:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這座城堡的事情\N我比你清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.68,0:08:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我幫你吧，可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有見過綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.52,0:08:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我聽說過她是在\N訓練期間在西塔失蹤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.09,0:08:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,訓練...\N是操控神機超重神的訓練嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過是用模擬器的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.56,0:08:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，那個就是\N綾香失去蹤影的西塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.30,0:08:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實要是沒有桑德曼的許可\N是不可以進去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.10,0:08:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸， 我們不會迷路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.87,0:08:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的\N我從小就住在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.64,0:08:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會迷路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.81,0:08:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從小?你家人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?是琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別，別這樣...不是啦別誤會啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.62,0:09:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫"死也不會偷看"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.79,0:09:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看在你是剛到城堡的份上\N想對你好一點的說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳誤會了...誤會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼誤會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.07,0:09:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個變態!色鬼、偷窺狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點琉菜，聽我說嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是誤會一場啦喔琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.12,0:09:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊，還真會到處亂跌耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.55,0:09:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡"跌倒"嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛跟來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很在意嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.53,0:10:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛G戰影的\N搞不好就是綾香吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.47,0:10:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也來這裡半年多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.64,0:10:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是有很多事情都搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.20,0:10:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼也不肯說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.37,0:10:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳，不是很早就住進來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.51,0:10:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是被桑德曼找來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.21,0:10:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前我只是在一般的學校上學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.95,0:10:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來的時候\N是綾香已經失蹤之後的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼，什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.00,0:10:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊，快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.83,0:10:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺，您在哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.78,0:10:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點給我滾出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.32,0:11:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛，又跌倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.09,0:11:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，看來很不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦，斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.60,0:11:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大事不妙了，桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.21,0:12:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺跟斗牙少爺\N還有琉菜小姐都不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.72,0:12:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南棟地下三樓A區，動作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.23,0:12:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人進去了\N所以觸發了機器人動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是斗牙他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.26,0:12:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上叫他們過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.57,0:12:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，真會挑時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.45,0:12:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽愛娜說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.72,0:12:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙小時候\N有個特訓設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.86,0:12:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙在嬰兒時期就失去了父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著被桑德曼所收留了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.73,0:12:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就一直在這座城堡裡受訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.17,0:12:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了因應外星異種來襲之時\N所設定的訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到昨天駕駛\N神機超重神出擊之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒踏出過城堡一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.94,0:13:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既沒有上學、也沒有朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.78,0:13:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到徹底的戰士訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.48,0:13:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然真的有耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.58,0:13:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了我之外也有其他的男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.25,0:13:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從小就一直在做這種事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.09,0:13:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也覺得他是個奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到真的是個奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險 斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過別動的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.98,0:13:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊，我是在幫你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.99,0:13:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的戰鬥能力太低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便亂動的話\N只會礙手礙腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.20,0:14:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請立即出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在斗牙他們過來之前\N可別大意哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.22,0:14:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.61,0:14:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺、琉菜小姐\N請快點過來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.11,0:14:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸...\N加儂的彈裝交換系統是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.53,0:15:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜!快逃!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.64,0:15:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.81,0:15:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G重鑽機，報告受損情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.75,0:15:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上部裝甲破損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.58,0:15:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右側飛彈裝置無法使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合神結構方面正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.99,0:15:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後部機座人員到達後\N立刻進入合神狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.76,0:15:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜，打開艙門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.39,0:15:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心一點，琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是，要好好的操控哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.31,0:15:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，這樣就沒有問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.41,0:15:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜，等您等了好久喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.08,0:15:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動合神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.64,0:17:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.71,0:17:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我軍已經進入備戰狀態了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您下令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.28,0:17:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有必要的話我們會提出請求的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還未到那種階段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.19,0:17:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，讓我們瞧瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的戰鬥實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獻醜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們地球戰騎隊的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.53,0:17:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半徑一公里範圍內\N的對人搜尋沒有反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.74,0:17:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居民已完成避難措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.21,0:18:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神機超重神重力子反應\N安定指數99%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.74,0:18:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距臨界點為止9988點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.48,0:18:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種的攻擊力以及防禦力\N應該都一起進化了才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不可大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.76,0:18:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重弧光!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.13,0:18:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重弧光被...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它進化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種正在放電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力系統傳達機能降下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.03,0:18:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子反應安定指數\N下降到64%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離臨界點為止7421點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電流啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.84,0:19:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員，使用各自負責的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.04,0:19:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對外星異種進行掃射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.45,0:19:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個渾蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧，超重飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全彈發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好，英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.98,0:19:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下子\N不准說我是礙手礙腳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.91,0:19:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.05,0:19:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離臨界點為止\N只剩下2022點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.69,0:19:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙，快使用超重劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.59,0:19:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.69,0:19:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.29,0:19:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劍身亮現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學終結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.52,0:20:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那..那是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.79,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然能在地面使用出\N威力這麼強大的武器...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考核通過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.24,0:20:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.85,0:20:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果，西塔還是沒去成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.32,0:21:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香真的還在這座城堡裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.76,0:21:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.82,0:21:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走著瞧吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.72,0:21:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會找出綾香\N跟這座城堡說掰掰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.10,0:21:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人真有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.03,0:21:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.04,0:21:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香，等著我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.72,0:21:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著在烈陽熱氣下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.40,0:21:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈現形形色色的擺動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.44,0:21:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知該為何這般\N心頭思緒紛亂不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.28,0:22:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就這麼視而不見\N朝向明日飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為無法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.86,0:22:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才說出了這麼不客氣的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.23,0:22:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤單一人地強出頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.03,0:22:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換來的只有誤解\N矛盾與迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.01,0:22:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於那牽繫著悲傷的羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.14,0:22:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓微笑的雙眸中滲出了淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.72,0:22:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想將這暖意傳送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.52,0:22:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便緊握著手一直不願放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.42,0:22:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好讓這祈禱得以傳達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.60,0:22:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺，救命啊\N有...有鬼出現了啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.17,0:22:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耍白痴啊，裘伊露妳是在作夢...\N哇!那是...那白影是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.57,0:22:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下...回播出"塔中的小公主"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.51,0:23:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下...週讓我們繼續照料\N各位的和平吧!